column2: AGM Group Holdings, Inc. engages in the provision of financial technology services. The firm mainly provides brokers and institutional clients with trading platform solutions and technologies. The firm operates mainly through three businesses, including online trading and computer support service business, which provides online trading platform application and computer program technical support and solution services; forex trading brokerage business, as well as program trading application technology and management service business. The firm operates its businesses in both the United Stated and global markets.
